FIRST TIME ONLY:
npm i 
npm install -g firebase-tools  <- installs firebase CLI tools on your terminal
firebase login
firebase projects:list <-- If you want to test your login then do this
my-cool-app should appear in your terminal. 

----
Change to 'deployment' branch

git merge main  <- to pull in most up to date changes
npm run build  <- create a build version
firebase deploy  <- deploy to firebase. 
---